x%2Fi%2FnNbBc5T.jpg&h=90c46601&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:35:22.000Z","msg":"我比較好奇即係唔係好似Kojima production / platinum 咁不歡而散？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:17:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://itw01.com/8OW9ECG.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitw01.com%2F8OW9ECG.html&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJuw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=056371e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://itw01.com/8OW9ECG.html</a><br />\n <br />\n1998年在『異度裝甲』還未和ENIX合併的SQUGRE在PlayStation上推出的新型別RPG遊戲，由製作人高橋哲哉領銜旗下小組製作，不過SQUARE因為FF movie大傷元氣，『異度裝甲』口碑雖好但表現一般，高橋的團隊基本上被架空了，異度系列繼續出續作也是個未知數，因為受到管理政策差異等原因，杉浦博英、高橋哲哉和本根康之從SQUARE退社，所以高橋的團隊出走，經過和一些遊戲公司的接觸，最終Namco向他們團隊拋來了橄欖枝，於是Monolith Soft就成了Namco的一個工作室。 原文網址：<a href=\"https://itw01.com/8OW9ECG.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitw01.com%2F8OW9ECG.html&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJuw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=056371e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itw01.com/8OW9ECG.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年既SQUARE 都俾ENIX 食左，變左SE啦，<br />\n我相信關係未到小島咁既地步既~~"},{"pid":"38b2cd95ac21265cb92d5de1268838ccc7bd4b7b","tid":1135694,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"Btw 現在玩到第八章<br />\n有冇需要買DLC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13bf0bb5e890c5847136b4cfc023bcb8a27ee0b","tid":1135694,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38b2cd95ac21265cb92d5de1268838ccc7bd4b7b","tid":1135694,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"Btw 現在玩到第八章<br />\n有冇需要買DLC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"DLC係前傳 講伊拉班人<br />\n爆左正傳先買都未遲"},{"pid":"55e3e906474ef3d328d8ceffe56eb6d778c76600","tid":1135694,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c13bf0bb5e890c5847136b4cfc023bcb8a27ee0b","